<br>
Little clarification..there are 4 Wings to the n/s/e/w of the lower courtyard, each with a boss.  Behind each boss is a porter that takes you to the upper courtyard with has a tower to the nw/sw/ne/se of the center.  The bosses I refer to enchanters soloing are the bosses at the tops of these towers, not the ones in the wings...no one really cares about that.<br>
<br>
I'm not even suggesting a charm nerf here...even if it is over-powered I don't really care.  Nerf them being able to bind up in the towers of BoT and I will be satisfied as long as they then watch for those already bound up there, and when the exploit is then performed the ench is promptly bound in PoT the moment they zone out by a GM. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.webspace.datanet.co.uk/cartwright/Docs/mage.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-family:BlackChancery;font-size:medium;">Ramierez D`Elerian Draegonis</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.webspace.datanet.co.uk/cartwright/Docs/mage.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:blue;font-family:Arial Narrow;font-size:x-small;">-A wizard's soul is forged in the crucible of magic~~Antimodes of the White Robes</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xandollf>xandollf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br>  Posts: 244<br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/22/02 12:00 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Anyone soloed in Bastion of Thunder?</span><hr size=1> You can solo if you can outnuke a non-summoning caster. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=102679">Xandollf</a><!--